data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bed, 2 bath home nestled on a desirable corner lot. This well-maintained residence offers comfortable living spaces and a prime location that combines convenience and tranquility. The home offers 3 spacious bedrooms, each offering a peaceful retreat. The master bedroom includes an ensuite bathroom for added privacy and convenience. The additional bedrooms are perfect for family members, guests, or a home office. One of the standout features of this property is the corner lot. Enjoy the benefits of increased privacy and abundant natural light simply relaxing in the sun on the side patio. Don't miss the opportunity to make the delightful corner home your own. Scheduled a viewing today and experience the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and charm.
